## Revision Requirements

{% if feedback.scope == 'hook' %}
Focus on revising the hook (first 3 seconds); keep the rest of the script as intact as possible.
{% elif feedback.scope == 'full_script' %}
Reorganize the entire script while preserving the core arguments and key information.
{% elif feedback.scope == 'tone' %}
Adjust the tone so it aligns more closely with the speaker's style profile.
{% elif feedback.scope == 'translation' %}
Retain the original meaning, but adjust the expression so it feels more natural.
{% endif %}

Reason mapping:
{% if feedback.reason == 'hook_not_catchy' %}
- The hook must be more impactful; use rhetorical questions, conflict, numbers, or counter-intuitive points
{% elif feedback.reason == 'not_like_speaker' %}
- Use the speaker's typical sentence structures and metaphors; avoid unfamiliar phrasing
{% elif feedback.reason == 'too_complex' %}
- Simplify the language, reduce jargon, and add analogies
{% elif feedback.reason == 'too_simple' %}
- Add depth, keep professional terminology, and increase information density
{% elif feedback.reason == 'factually_inaccurate' %}
- Strictly adhere to the facts in the original segment; do not add information not present in the source text
{% elif feedback.reason == 'different_expression' %}
- Adjust the expression while keeping the original meaning
{% endif %}

